const page = ['home', 'product', 'cart', 'blog', 'contact', '404']
let collection
fetch('https://fakestoreapi.com/products')
  .then(res => res.json())
  .then(json => collection = [...json])
const color = ['red', 'white', 'blue', 'black', 'pink']
const popularTags = ['black', 'blue', 'browm', 'l', 'm', 'ml', 'pink', 'sky', 'white', 'x', 'xl']

export {page, color, popularTags}
export default collection
